;; A Sudoku puzzle is a grid of 81 squares; the majority of enthusiasts
;; label the columns 1-9, the rows A-I, and call a collection of nine
;; squares (column, row, or box) a unit and the squares that share a unit
;; the peers.

(in-package #:sudoku)

